-- query58
WITH ss_items 
 AS (SELECT i_item_id item_id, 
 Sum(ss_ext_sales_price) ss_item_rev 
 FROM store_sales, 
 item, 
 date_dim 
 WHERE ss_item_sk = i_item_sk 
 AND d_date IN (SELECT d_date 
 FROM date_dim 
 WHERE d_week_seq = (SELECT d_week_seq 
 FROM date_dim 
 WHERE d_date = '2002-02-25' 
 )) 
 AND ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk 
 GROUP BY i_item_id), 
 cs_items 
 AS (SELECT i_item_id item_id, 
 Sum(cs_ext_sales_price) cs_item_rev 
 FROM catalog_sales, 
 item, 
 date_dim 
 WHERE cs_item_sk = i_item_sk 
 AND d_date IN (SELECT d_date 
 FROM date_dim 
 WHERE d_week_seq = (SELECT d_week_seq 
 FROM date_dim 
 WHERE d_date = '2002-02-25' 
 )) 
 AND cs_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk 
 GROUP BY i_item_id), 
 ws_items 
 AS (SELECT i_item_id item_id, 
 Sum(ws_ext_sales_price) ws_item_rev 
 FROM web_sales, 
 item, 
 date_dim 
 WHERE ws_item_sk = i_item_sk 
 AND d_date IN (SELECT d_date 
 FROM date_dim 
 WHERE d_week_seq = (SELECT d_week_seq 
 FROM date_dim 
 WHERE d_date = '2002-02-25' 
 )) 
 AND ws_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk 
 GROUP BY i_item_id) 
SELECT ss_items.item_id, 
 ss_item_rev, 
 ss_item_rev / ( ss_item_rev + cs_item_rev + ws_item_rev ) / 3 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup 
 100 ss_dev, 
 cs_item_rev, 
 cs_item_rev / ( ss_item_rev + cs_item_rev + ws_item_rev ) / 3 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup 
 100 cs_dev, 
 ws_item_rev, 
 ws_item_rev / ( ss_item_rev + cs_item_rev + ws_item_rev ) / 3 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup 
 100 ws_dev, 
 ( ss_item_rev + cs_item_rev + ws_item_rev ) / 3 
 average 
FROM ss_items, 
 cs_items, 
 ws_items 
WHERE ss_items.item_id = cs_items.item_id 
 AND ss_items.item_id = ws_items.item_id 
 AND ss_item_rev BETWEEN 0.9 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup cs_item_rev AND 1.1 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup cs_item_rev 
 AND ss_item_rev BETWEEN 0.9 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup ws_item_rev AND 1.1 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup ws_item_rev 
 AND cs_item_rev BETWEEN 0.9 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup ss_item_rev AND 1.1 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup ss_item_rev 
 AND cs_item_rev BETWEEN 0.9 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup ws_item_rev AND 1.1 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup ws_item_rev 
 AND ws_item_rev BETWEEN 0.9 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup ss_item_rev AND 1.1 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup ss_item_rev 
 AND ws_item_rev BETWEEN 0.9 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup cs_item_rev AND 1.1 Readme.md benchmark.sh bootstrap.sh data_gen.sh load_data.sh query results tpc-ds-data-gen warmup cs_item_rev 
ORDER BY item_id, 
 ss_item_rev
LIMIT 100;
